<%@ page pageEncoding="UTF-8" %>
<section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.7226666666666666" src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-01.jpg" data-w="750" type="block"  /></section><section><div class="lf-audio-card"><i class="fa fa-volume-up"></i><div><b>&#38899;&#39057;&#65306;</b>&#36335;&#39118;-&#33402;&#28023;&#27969;&#20809;&#65288;&#19979;&#65289;<br/><span>&#21407;&#33410;&#30446;&#38899;&#39057;&#26102;&#38271;&#21487;&#36890;&#36807;&#21407;&#24494;&#20449;&#25991;&#31456;&#25910;&#21548;&#12290;</span></div></div></section><section><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size:17.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">文学、摄影与多媒介艺术</span><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">主持人：您的游记写作达几十万字，并且是作家协会活跃会员，您在“美篇”上是热门摄影博主，如此丰富多彩的艺术人生，如此多元的艺术表现力，您是如何看待绘画，写作与摄影三者的关系？</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">路风：</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">绘画、写作、摄影是三个不同的独立的艺术表现形式。绘画是创作者通过颜料等工具在平面上创造形象，侧重于主观的想象和表现。摄影是记录“真实存在”的影像，侧重于展现和构图。写作则是用语言文字来表达思想和情感，媒介是文字，而不仅仅是视觉。个人认为，他们有一个共同的特点，都是通过观察世界，记录世界，想象世界，一个人独立完成的艺术创作形式。</span></p><span leaf="" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">从2016年入驻美篇以来，至今我发布了613篇文章，其中248篇成为美篇精选文章。这些文章包括了我的世界各地摄影采风的游记、教学论文、在报刊发表的散文小说、学生画展、学生摄影展，以及春夏秋冬的散文摄影作品。《大年初一走黄刀约会北极光》《远方的诗-阿拉斯加》《看一眼敦煌》《我和福娃传圣火》《冰岛采风之旅（手机拍摄）》《风景写生夏令营（手机拍摄）》《初秋鸥影（手机拍摄）》《十年一遇的超级蓝月亮（手机拍摄）》等文章深受读者喜爱。</span></p><span leaf="" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">&nbsp;2024年11月被中央新影中学生频道《榜样力量》栏目组，在美篇茫茫人海中与我结缘，并为我精心制作了《文化影响力》中国艺术家档案--路风，于2025年1月18号历时四天的中央新影中学生频道、CCTV手机电视、咪咕视频、电视家及其他电视直播平台，《榜样力量》官方网站、中学生频道官方网站，首播一天和重播三天。</span></p><span leaf="" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">&nbsp;2025年3月被中国华夏文化研究院授予《两会重点推荐艺术家称号》</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">&nbsp;2025年3月7号被推选为《文创时代》非遗双创人才。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">2025年5月29号被中央新影中学生频道《文创时代》授予《抗战胜利80周年文化传承楷模》出版《路风绘画摄影作品集》。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">因在书画创作、摄影艺术领域取得的成就，2025年5月被中国华夏文化研究院批 准收加入“全国首批智库专家成员团”。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">2025年9月作品被《文创时代》收入《2025品牌影响力名家大师》一书出版。</span></p></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></section><p style=""><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-02.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.4785714285714286" data-w="280" height="331" style="width:277px;height:410px;" width="224"  /></span><span style="mso-no-proof:yes;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-03.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.7260869565217392" data-w="230" height="318" style="width:232px;height:400px;" width="184"  /></span></span><span style="mso-tab-count:1;"></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=""><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-no-proof:yes;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;<img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-04.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.6059701492537313" data-w="335" height="430" width="268"  /><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.5248447204968945" src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-05.jpg" data-w="322" height="393" style="width:282px;height:430px;" width="258"  /></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:
&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-06.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.1363636363636365" data-w="286" height="260" style="width:392px;height:445px;" width="229"  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-07.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7960893854748603" data-w="358" height="228" style="width:402px;height:320px;" width="286"  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-08.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.6361829025844931" data-w="503" height="256" width="402"  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">主持人：您的作品《驶过冰山绿地》获得金奖，&nbsp;</span><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">能否谈谈这个作品的创作背景和创作灵感？</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left;" data-pm-slice="3 3 []"><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">路风：2023</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">年</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">9</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">月</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">6</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">号启程历时十八天，去冰岛挪威手机摄影采风，回来写了十八章游记发布在美篇，和一篇《冰岛手机摄影采风之旅驶过冰山绿地》在加州版《中国日报》上发表。全部成为精选文章。手机摄影作品《驶过冰上绿地》在《摄影名家》在线影展中荣获，金奖。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes;"></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">路风：坐落在山脉和峡湾之间的塞济斯菲厄泽，因其明信片般的上镜效果，成为冰岛最美丽的村庄之一。二零二零年人口统计六百八十人。历史悠久、建筑风格独具特色的蓝色教堂是冰岛的地标。彩虹路、艺术画廊、人们装饰房屋和花园、雪崩纪念碑、二零二零年十二月山体滑坡地址以及该地区众多迷人的瀑布，是了解当地人文景观的要点。</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span></span></p><p style=""><span lang="ZH-CN" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">下午五点钟当游轮启程的时候，呈现在我眼前的是：蓝天下雪山之巅连绵起伏的山脉，瀑布的脉络从天而降如丝线般绣出山体魁梧的肌理线条；峡湾之间巍巍群山下的绿地上住着几栋白色墙壁天蓝色、橘红色屋顶彩色的房子，既恬静又充满朝气和童趣的欢快。一艘白色的游艇划开镜面一般的山峦倒影溅起洁白的浪花缓缓而行，《驶过冰山绿地》。融春夏秋冬为一体的动感景观，这是何等壮美而又柔情似水的画面啊！有备而来的我立刻用手机按下快门！十月二十号我收到了九州摄影举办的</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">“</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">摄影名家在线影展</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">”</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">邀请函，《驶过冰山绿地》以清晰的画质，明快的色彩，巧妙的构思，反映世界大自然瑰宝冰岛名山大川的画面荣获手机摄影金奖</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf="">。</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=""><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.4717223650385604" src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-09.jpg" data-w="778" height="294" width="622"  /></span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=""><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-10.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.702954898911353" data-w="643" height="362" width="514"  /></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.5pt;font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;color: rgb(36, 36, 36);"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span></p><section data-pm-slice="3 3 []"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size:17.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">非遗与未来</span></span></span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:17.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">——</span></span></span></b><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size:17.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">当代艺术家的文化使命</span></span></span></b></section><section><b style="font-weight:normal;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">主持人：少数民族文化如何影响和塑造了您的艺术理念？</span></span></h2><span leaf="" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">路风：77年高考，78年2月入学广西艺术学院美术系装潢专业。绘画基本功教学在一、二年级的上半学期进行，下半学期肩背铺盖画具到桂林、阳朔、兴坪风景写生，日晒雨淋，睡文化宫的课桌椅，电影院尚未完工的毛呸房；大学三年级到大瑶山少数民族地区体验生活，和瑶族村民同吃，同住一个吊楼，一同生活。他们腾出最好的房间，阁楼上的单间让我们两位同专业的女生住。零距离地观赏瑶族姐妹用美好寓意的图案为自己刺绣嫁妆。大瑶山里环境潮湿我水土不服，腹痛卧床不起。瑶家主人知道到后，让瑶妹端上来一杯灰色的水说：“你喝下这杯水就好了。”看着颜色灰暗的水我问道：“这是什么水？”“你不要问，你喝下就肚子不疼了。”瑶妹笑着说。于是，我一口气喝下去那杯仙水，一会儿，我的肚子果然不疼了。我起身下到吊楼的堂屋，瑶妹指着堂屋中烧火的草木灰说；“你刚才喝的是草木灰水。”原来少数民族家中的灵丹妙药就是身边的一草一木。他们的智慧令人惊叹和钦佩，在与村民的相处时让人感受到纯洁的爱。此次体验生活，我创作了装饰画系列：织布、挑担、播种、梳妆、插秧、筛谷。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">返校途经柳州时，将其中的一两幅作品在广西柳州日报上发表，获得稿费赚到我的第一桶金。在高校任教时将它们设计成桂林火柴包装，荣获1987年广西包协包装装潢设计委员会颁发的“广西优秀包装设计奖”。少数民族的生活、风俗、文化在我的学生时代就成为了我创作的源泉。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color: transparent;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;text-decoration: none;vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden;width: 432px;height: 248px;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-11.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.5740740740740741" data-w="540" height="248" style="margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;width:432px;height:248px;" width="432"  /></span></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color: transparent;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;text-decoration: none;vertical-align: baseline;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">1980年在龙胜瑶族山区体验生活，</span></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color: transparent;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;text-decoration: none;vertical-align: baseline;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">和村民们同吃、同住、身着姑娘们刺绣的民族服装留影，</span></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color: transparent;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;text-decoration: none;vertical-align: baseline;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">我们已然成为好朋友。左二、路风。</span></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color: transparent;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;text-decoration: none;vertical-align: baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">在大瑶山区体验生活，我创作了装饰画系列：织布、挑担、播种、梳妆、插秧、筛谷。于1980年在广西柳州日报上发表。1987设计成桂林火柴包装，荣获广西包协包装装潢设计委员会颁发的‘广西优秀包装设计奖’’。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color: transparent;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;text-decoration: none;vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden;width: 459px;height: 328px;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-12.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7167832167832168" data-w="572" height="328" style="margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;" width="459"  /></span></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">2018年回国探亲，参加80周年学院校庆，音乐学院苗族同学接待我们。回来后从照片中看见其羞涩、秀色美丽的容貌让人感动，忍不住用几支彩色铅笔即兴作画（下图），在朋友圈发布后收到了一片赞扬声。于是，我开始了《回眸一笑百媚生-路风彩色铅笔画人物系列》创作。2019年2月到广西大苗山体验生活，参加苗族庆典。同年6月到欧洲波罗的海，丹麦哥本哈根，爱沙尼亚塔林，7月去英国伦敦，温莎城堡，爱丁堡，12月到美国的夏威夷采风。体验所到之处少数民族生活文化风俗，准备创作《回眸一笑百媚生-路风彩色铅笔画人物系列》，从广西苗族扩展到世界各地少数民族。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color: transparent;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;text-decoration: none;vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden;width: 265px;height: 356px;"><span leaf=""><img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-13.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.3444108761329305" data-w="331" height="356" style="margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;width:261px;height:351px;" width="265"  /></span></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color: transparent;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;text-decoration: none;vertical-align: baseline;"><span leaf="">《回眸一笑百媚生-路风彩色铅笔画人物系列（一）》</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">主持人：您如何看待非遗的当代创新？</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">路风：当历史叩响新时代大门，我们既要以虔敬之心守护技艺的原真性，更要以创新之志激活其当代生命力-- “创造性转化，创新性发展”，以双手为舟楫，载着古老技艺穿越时代洪流：以创新为星火，点燃非遗基因的当代觉醒。从绘画和摄影来说，使用同一个画种的工具，比如油画、中国画、水彩画，写生或者创作出来的必定是新的作品。摄影也如此，用相机、手机拍摄的所见所闻，也一定是与从前有所不同的。所以，在这两种艺术形式的表现上，是作者新的构思和情感与时代的步伐同步或者超前的自然流露，就是创作的过程。文学也是这样。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">关于来自仫佬族文化的审美与技艺启蒙。我能够成为仫佬族的后代，非常荣幸。我的奶奶是仫佬族，奶奶和爷爷离乡背井来到城市来打拼，虽然奶奶在我很小的时候就去世了，但是，她的勤俭持家、温柔善良、和看顾我和弟弟的场景，像一幅温馨的图画存留在我的脑海里......仫佬族现有27万多人口，有自己的语言，使用汉字，历史悠久可以追溯到元代以前。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">主持人：非遗的“创造性转化”在北美社会具有怎样的可能性？ &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">路风：</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">当代艺术家在"非遗与未来"的议题中肩负着重要的文化使命, 包括通过创新性表达传承非遗文化, 使其在当代社会焕发新的生命力。他们的使命还包括利用非遗的"精神养分"和"历史根基"来构建民族精神, 并通过现代艺术的手段促进非遗融入现代生活, 让"非遗" 在未来发展中扮演更重要的角色。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">非遺在北美社会具有巨大的可能性、 但需克服一些挑战、 如文化挪用和商业化。可行方案包括： 通过跨文化合作实现非遗与现代设计的融合、 将非遺技艺转化 为现代生活用品和艺术品;利用数字化技术、通过虛拟现实、3D建模等方式、 将非遗内容进行现代化呈现和普及; 强调非遗背后的人文价值、 在教育、旅游等领域推广非遗文化、以促进理解和欣赏。创新性传承与发展：艺术家将传统非遗技艺和观念, 例如剪纸、绘画、书法，摄影等, 通过现代艺术的视角进行再创作, 使其在当代语境下焕发新的活力和美感。构建民族精神： &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 艺术家通过作品喚醒大众对民族文化的认同感, 将非遗视为民族精神和文化认同的积淀, 从而为建设先进文化提供思想和精神上的根基。在提倡多元文化的北美，展示非遗民族文化的魅力。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;"><br  /></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">主持人：非常感谢路风老师的精彩分享，在节目的最后，请您谈谈</span><b style="text-align: left;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">您未来在渥太华的文化计划有哪些？</span></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;">路风：在渥太华华人社区举办的各种画展、现场剪纸、绘画、书法展示、生肖绘画比赛、民族歌舞、器乐演奏等等，是华人非遗技艺在多元文化舞台上的直观展示和交流。希望这些活动能够继续举办。我也希望，有朝一日我的《回眸一笑百媚生-路风彩色铅笔画人物系列》在渥太华举办的个人画展，，通过呈现苗族静美的银饰与精湛的刺绣等民族服饰，为观众带来美的享受。</span></p></b></section><p style="text-align: left;" data-pm-slice="4 1 []"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="">（采编主持：灵兮）</span></span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.3328125" src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-14.jpg" data-w="1280" type="block"  /></section><section><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size:17.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;"><span leaf="" data-pm-slice="0 0 []" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">CHINRADIO 97.9FM 渥太华中文电台</span></span><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">，由CHIN RADIO和渥太华华人社区服务中心联合主办，岁月如歌文艺沙龙协办，感谢您的关注和分享，欢迎留言点评。</span></span></b></span></b></section><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-lufeng-part2/lufeng-part2-15.png" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7084639498432602" data-w="319" type="block"  /></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p>